headline: Deere (DE) Declares US$1.62 Quarterly Dividend For November 2025 Payout
summary: Deere (DE) recently affirmed a quarterly dividend of $1.62 per share, set for distribution in November. This announcement aligns with positive movements in major indices, as the S&P 500 reached an all-time high and the Dow Jones approached record levels. While Deere's share price remained relatively flat over the week, the dividend declaration added a stabilizing factor amid modest broader market growth. headline: OneTrust Announces Speaker Lineup for TrustWeek 2025 US Cities
summary: OneTrust today announced the keynote and breakout session speaker lineup for its TrustWeek 2025 events in New York and San Francisco. TrustWeek is the company's flagship event, bringing leaders together to explore real-world solutions for responsible innovation — balancing speed, scale, and accountability in the age of AI.
